		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As a newbie to nes dev, what is the best emulator source code to use as a starting point for new development?
<br />
<br />C/C++ language using MS visual studio/Windows is my preferred environment . 
<br />
<br />Djgpp is second.

		

